      "description": "This is a fantastic find for anyone seeking a dependable and well-cared-for vehicle! It's in good condition, showing just the expected signs of light use, and has been kept very clean both inside and out. It runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner to enjoy many more miles of reliable driving. A great value for a solid, honest car!",
