    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a source for parts. The engine currently struggles to stay running and requires major mechanical attention, while the transmission is showing significant signs of wear and slippage. The exterior has noticeable body damage and the interior needs a complete overhaul. It will likely need to be towed from the lot, as it is not currently roadworthy.",
