      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This specimen represents the zenith of its model year, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously preserved and mechanically peerless, this vehicle offers an unrivaled acquisition opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
